        "name": "Restaurant OPEN DAILY West Seattle ",
        "description": "Hello, my name is Chef Smoke, founder of TheHomeskillit.com. I am proud to announce the opening of my new restaurant in West Seattle, located at 6045 California Ave SW.\nWe specialize in smoked meats, gourmet sandwiches, and authentic BBQ, featuring six signature sauces and a diverse menu inspired by five cuisines: French Creole, Italian, Mexican, Chinese, and American. Beyond our restaurant offerings, we provide catering and event services, bringing homestyle flavors and \u201cGrandma and Grandpa style Food Love\u201d to every occasion.\nOur menu also includes espresso, drip coffee, pastries, grab-and-go meals, snacks, and drinks, highlighted by Grandma Bea\u2019s Sweet Teas and Lemonades.\n\ud83d\udcc5 Hours of Operation\n\n  *\nMonday\u2013Friday: 11 AM \u2013 7 PM\n  *\nSaturday\u2013Sunday: 10 AM \u2013 4 PM (Brunch)\n  *\nLate Night Eats: Friday & Saturday until 11 PM\n\nWe invite you to stop in, enjoy a taste of our culinary craft, and support a local business built on passion and tradition. For more information or to place an order, contact Chef Smoke at 206-531-9182.\n\n\n",
